name: MathQuiz
0:
”Alexa, ask Math Wiz to start game”
”Alexa, start math wiz”
”Alexa, begin math wiz”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: math wiz
des: A simple math quiz with multiplication factors (numbers 1-10). During the game Alexa keeps track of how many questions you get right and wrong. At the end, Alexa will tell you how many you got right out of how many questions were asked.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
